title: Week 3 Studs & Duds + Jason Melts Down, Monday Punday - Fantasy Football Podcast for 9/26
description:
Jason is tilting! On today’s fantasy football podcast, a Week 3 review of the biggest studs and duds! Which dud performances are actually concerning? Which Week 3 fantasy football studs will do it again? Plus, big injury news and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for September 26th, 2022.
